Class BTOProj

java.lang.Object
sg.edu.ntu.sc2002.ay2425.fcsdGroup2.model.entities.BTOProj
public class BTOProj extends Object
Represents a Build-To-Order (BTO) project managed by HDB. Contains project details, flats, applications, officers, and enquiries.
